data.description: Welcome Home to this turn of the Century craftsman home in Historic Colonial Place. Mins to VA Zoo, NFK Railroad District, cafes, shops & ODU. This charming home has original hardwood floors w/extensive wood trim. Updated for today w/a brand new kitchen to include: slow close cabinets, granite counters, LVP floor and more, w/an oversized pantry for all your storage needs. 2nd floor HVAC/air handler 2020, downstairs Gas/Electric dual htg/cooling unit 2013. 16 double paned low E windows 2015. Gutters 2016. Complete encapsulation of crawl space for storage (done by JES) with dehumidifier 2014. Detached Garage 2022. Sump Pump 2024. Finish the attic for additional living space!
